&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#5%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%83%E5%B1%82%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95&#34;&gt;（5）基于双通路跃层卷积网络的交通标志识别算法&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
